Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.82,0:03:43.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我想开会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:45.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,举行职员会议吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:47.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,来开编辑会议了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.03,0:03:48.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:53.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,当作是为了交流去参加也是为人着想了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:55.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,交流很重要嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.54,0:04:01.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不过…会来担心我的家庭会议什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.76,0:04:03.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,大家意外的都是好人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:07.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,会来担心我的编辑会议什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:09.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,大家意外的都是好人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.72,0:04:12.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,会来担心我的职员会议什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.02,0:04:14.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,大家意外的都是好人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.23,0:04:18.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不过说到底  果然还是想尽可能的不开会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:20.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:22.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,话说…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:25.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这个  是啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:27.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老井…吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.99,0:04:28.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,应该是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.99,0:04:31.37,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\pos(839.4,780.4)}是井边会议
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.99,0:04:31.37,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,注：在日本江户时代住在平房的主妇们经常能在取水洗衣的时候在水井处遇见，所以在井口旁聊起家常八卦的现象\N非常普遍，后被称之为「井边会议」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:33.87,kakushigoto in 2,,0,0,0,,{\frz333.1\pos(907.2,592)}最终回无动于衷的她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:33.87,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,注：标题源自高桥真的漫画「最终兵器女友」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.33,0:04:35.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.62,0:04:36.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.33,0:04:37.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:41.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,会议室什么时候能做好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.30,0:04:45.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,难道说真的有需要开会解决的议题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:49.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,能…能作为参考说说是什么议题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:51.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是关于生日聚会的事情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:53.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,竟然是生日聚会？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.56,0:04:57.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不是  带会议室的家很少见的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:04:59.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.44,0:05:01.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,至少咱家里没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:05.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,没有会议室也能开会的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.78,0:05:06.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那多不像样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:10.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我一直都以为会议得在会议室开才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:11.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在哪儿都行么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:12.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,水井
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:15.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是叫「井边会议」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:17.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,找到水井的话就能开会了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:20.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,水井在东京还有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:22.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.46,0:05:27.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是要委托寻找水井  这么理解可以么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:28.30,kakushigoto in 10 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\frz266.9\pos(817.6,555.2)}目黑川侦探事务所
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.68,0:05:32.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这个委托  就由目黑川侦探事务所接下了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:35.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我也是所员啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.98,0:05:38.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.02,0:05:41.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,竟然是关于生日聚会的会议
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.82,0:05:44.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬的生日  应该还有半年以上才对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.94,0:05:46.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好  确认了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.49,0:05:49.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这周也谢谢您了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:50.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.49,0:05:52.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我要进行料理的特训
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.91,0:05:57.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,变得能炸出怎么吃都吃不完的美味炸鸡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.37,0:06:01.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不相信那个时候我说的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:05.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,对了对了  多亏了您编辑会议平安结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.09,0:06:08.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,开过编辑会议了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:11.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您不是还担心过的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:13.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,为什么我要担心编辑会…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:15.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.97,0:06:15.72,kakushigoto in 5,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\c&H787776&\frz2.139\pos(462.4,147.2)}议题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.97,0:06:15.72,kakushigoto in 5,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\c&H777777&\frz1.441\pos(467.2,222.4)}连载阵容的更替
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.89,0:06:18.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这家店似乎很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:19.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但好像也挺贵呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:21.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:26.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,于是呢  主编问您下次要不要去吃好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.86,0:06:29.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,主编亲自叫人出来…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.32,0:06:32.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是吗  终于…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.66,0:06:33.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要腰斩了么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:35.74,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}腰斩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.16,0:06:39.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真好啊  和主编一起去吃好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.21,0:06:41.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要去高档的馆子吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.96,0:06:42.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.34,0:06:46.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,主编专门请人去吃好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:48.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎么可能是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.17,0:06:50.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,做好觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:58.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,于是呢  后藤老师说下次去吃个饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.19,0:07:03.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,什么情况  是什么待遇上的不满么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:06.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真讨厌啊  和作者发生争执什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:07.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那…那个么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:10.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,说起来好几年都没给安排彩页了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.24,0:07:12.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那么我就去订店了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:29.42,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}大吃特吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:29.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真好吃啊  这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.71,0:07:31.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然是腰斩吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:34.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,具体是到多久呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.01,0:07:35.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}虎躯一震
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.60,0:07:38.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}果然是要求画彩页吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:40.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是…是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:42.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,尽可能快点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:45.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}再怎么快也得四周以后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.81,0:07:46.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,尽可能快点？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:49.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}这么突然故事结不了尾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.86,0:07:52.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这个是什么做的啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.82,0:07:56.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,能十周之后就很感激了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.33,0:07:58.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这么后面么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:08:00.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然太后面了么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.37,0:08:04.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,没有没有  这种程度的话我也能准备了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.62,0:08:05.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,准备？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:06.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,关于什么的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.88,0:08:07.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:09.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,彩页啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:13.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,彩页…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:15.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.76,0:08:18.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.51,0:08:21.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,谢谢您的关怀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.73,0:08:27.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,太好了呢  不知为何拿到了彩页
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.11,0:08:30.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就跟分手费差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:37.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,用彩页来完美收场  基本的人文关怀啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.32,0:08:37.62,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,700)\fs50\bord4\c&H32F5EE&\3c&H49495D&\frz21.27\move(280,697.6,281.2,587)}感动的最终回
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.32,0:08:37.62,kakushigoto in 4,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,700)\bord3\frz275\c&HC26E88&\move(502.4,838.4,503.2,711.6)}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.03,0:08:43.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,请旗下担任的作家吃饭  还拿到了彩页
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.50,0:08:46.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我是个多么优秀的责编啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.00,0:08:48.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这么贵的馆子的收据
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:51.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不是主编的话很难报销
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.76,0:08:56.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,该怎么对大家说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.22,0:08:59.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是帮他们找好下家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.51,0:09:03.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,还是支付工资  等到下一部连载再开呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.39,0:09:07.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不  下一部连载要到何时
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.69,0:09:09.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在哪本杂志上连载都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:14.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,收入也断了  这样的话钱再多都不够
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.78,0:09:21.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,连载的间隙对漫画家来说可谓是逢魔之时
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:26.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不游下去就会死去的鱼  要是放弃游动的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.67,0:09:29.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,想要再次游起来就不容易了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.59,0:09:33.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,恍惚之间一年过去了  两年过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:36.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,被读者和编辑们所忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.39,0:09:42.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,中断的收入  持续下去的经费
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:44.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,眼看着储蓄减少
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:46.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,却看不见光明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.10,0:09:50.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,然后身心状态变得不稳定的漫画家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:53.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,会变得越来越想不出有趣的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:55.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,陷入恶性循环
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:09:59.49,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fs75\frx34\fry352\frz33.79\move(873.6,249.6,72.8,249.4)}账单
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:10:00.62,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\frx26\fry352\frz27.84\move(1502.4,307.2,314.6,310.4,0,3486)}需支付金额  210000日元
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:10:00.62,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\frx26\fry352\frz31.73\move(1556.8,723.2,380,712.8,0,3486)}租船费  1艘  80000日元
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:10:00.62,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\frx26\fry352\frz33.84\move(1624,926.4,465,906.6,0,3486)}潜水员费  2名  53000日元
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:10:00.62,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\frx26\fry352\frz33.84\move(1868.8,1049.6,687.4,1044.2,24,3486)}燃料费  1套  10000日元
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.45,0:09:59.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,即便不那样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.07,0:10:02.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也要花钱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.51,0:10:19.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.68,0:10:23.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,被炉真是可怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:26.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,等爸爸的时候不知何时意识就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.18,0:10:28.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在被炉睡觉会感冒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:32.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,对了  我忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.82,0:10:35.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,欢迎回家  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.78,0:10:40.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我回来了  姬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.78,0:10:43.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,虽然不知道未来的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.37,0:10:46.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但作为父亲在姬的面前还是以笑脸面对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:48.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:54.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,「风之紧身裤」还有十周就将完结了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.00,0:10:56.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.42,0:10:58.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真遗憾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:11:02.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你们也不吃惊一下  不伤感一下么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.64,0:11:05.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,为什么要  总有一天会完结的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.64,0:11:07.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,稍微也失落一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:09.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你们不也会因为失去工作而困扰么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.31,0:11:13.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,差不多想要些时间画自己作品了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.23,0:11:14.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.52,0:11:20.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我也差不多该好好去大学了  不拿到学分毕不了业
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:21.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:24.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我们的事情  请不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:27.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.24,0:11:29.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.54,0:11:31.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,顾虑我的心情而故意的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.21,0:11:32.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.33,0:11:36.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好  最后的冲刺了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.71,0:11:38.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一直画到完结吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.51,0:11:43.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,现在我该做的  那便是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.64,0:11:45.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,集中于漫画之上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.80,0:11:47.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,说是刚刚好…虽然有点那啥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:51.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,请让我放假…有点难说出口呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.52,0:11:51.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:54.98,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\pos(275.2,256)}※\h\h意外的是这种理由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.73,0:12:01.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,居然亲口发出了拟声词
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:03.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这就是老师他全神贯注的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:05.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,嗯  看上去有些瘆人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.37,0:12:09.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,反正也要完了  那就想画什么就画吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.58,0:12:11.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,大干一场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:18.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,喂  十丸院
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.67,0:12:22.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,最近的风之紧身裤突然变得有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.22,0:12:23.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:27.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然说了给他彩页过后他就有干劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:28.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.51,0:12:30.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,当腰斩定下来的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.06,0:12:33.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,像这样漫画突然变得有趣了的情况也时有发生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:39.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,太有趣了  但这梗也太狠了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:42.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师您这是全面开战  完全不怕死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.32,0:12:45.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,哈哈  反正都要完结了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:49.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,无后顾之忧的漫画家犹如受伤的狼一样奋死一搏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:52.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这周的原稿也很有灵性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.41,0:12:54.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这下  紧身裤也就不用担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.91,0:12:56.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.58,0:13:00.25,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,毕竟有像我这么优秀的责编
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:04.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,无后顾之忧的漫画家通常会超常发挥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.05,0:13:08.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我打算去欧洲旅游一周
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.47,0:13:09.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.01,0:13:12.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但前提是要能够完结
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.81,0:13:16.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我们终于  发现了这口井
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.77,0:13:18.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,嗯  找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.73,0:13:21.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,现在开井边会议还太冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.11,0:13:23.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,还没什么人使用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.07,0:13:26.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也就是会议随便开喽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:28.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.45,0:13:31.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我得和爸爸开家庭会议了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.12,0:13:34.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:36.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我们可以开家庭会议了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.04,0:13:41.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,糟了  因为腰斩的事情完全搞忘了这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:43.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:47.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,因为最近忙工作  还没来得及修建会议室
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.55,0:13:49.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,没事的  我找到会场了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.39,0:13:51.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,会场？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:54.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,反正都是家里的某处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.43,0:13:53.14,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\fs50\frz336\pos(500.8,380.8)\c&H727377&}会议中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:53.14,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\fs50\c&H626468&\pos(580.8,97.6)\frz356.5}比如这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.18,0:13:54.89,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\fs50\c&H727377&\pos(571.2,464)\frz24.08}会议中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.14,0:13:54.89,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\c&H626468&\frz356.5\pos(328,638.4)}比如这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.56,0:13:56.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但  确实…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.27,0:14:00.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,必须得开家庭会议了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.94,0:14:02.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,因为我快失业了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.44,0:14:04.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,即使没了工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:08.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我也不会让姬担心和感到不安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.07,0:14:09.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,无论发生什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:12.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬期待着的生日聚会  我也要举办给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:14.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,失业了又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.50,0:14:16.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.87,0:14:19.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,等明天下班后  我们来开家庭会议吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.34,0:14:27.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原稿我收下了  这周也同样很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.42,0:14:28.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,应该吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:30.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那么再见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:46.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,得赶紧回去了  不能让姬担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:48.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.82,0:14:50.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,欢迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.03,0:14:51.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.49,0:14:52.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:56.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我先去准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.25,0:14:58.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我们走吧  洛克
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:05.29,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\c&H6C55C2&\3c&HF6DBFB&\b1\move(516,330,506,254,0,1818)\frz10.84}家庭会议  指引图
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:05.29,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\c&H6C55C2&\3c&HE3E3E3&\b1\frz22.4\move(134,510,24,456,0,1818)}小学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:05.29,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\c&H6C55C2&\3c&HF6DBFB&\frz10.05\b1\move(750,802,660,732,0,1818)}河
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:05.29,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\c&H6C55C2&\3c&HFDFDE1&\frz12.3\b1\move(1448,646,1358,572,0,1818)}会场
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:05.29,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\c&H6C55C2&\3c&HF9FFD8&\frz10.05\b1\move(1462,966,1380,890,0,1818)}井
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:05.29,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\c&H6C55C2&\3c&H72E290&\b1\frz14.37\move(1616,922,1530,848,0,1818)}公园
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.29,0:15:04.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,井
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.59,0:15:07.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原来是井边会议啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.21,0:15:09.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这样确实能够开会了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:15.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要掉下去了怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.06,0:15:19.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是姬的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.23,0:15:21.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬  你掉下去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.11,0:15:26.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,没…掉下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.48,0:15:27.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那为什么你要大叫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.78,0:15:29.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,里边儿有声音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:30.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,声音？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.24,0:15:34.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,1张  2张
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.53,0:15:38.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}3张…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:40.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这里不是番町皿屋敷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:43.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您搞错地方出没了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:43.17,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,注：番町皿屋敷是指夜晚亡灵在井里数碟子的日本传统鬼故事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:43.17,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,日语中张和枚发音相同
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:48.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,4张  5张
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.63,0:15:50.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,快逃  姬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:53.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}6张  7张
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.42,0:15:51.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是  爸爸你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.47,0:15:53.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,洛克  快走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.39,0:15:56.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.01,0:15:56.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}8张…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.64,0:15:58.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,9张…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.06,0:16:02.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,10…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.23,0:16:05.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,张
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.19,0:16:09.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师  我找回了10张
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.49,0:16:17.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原稿是16张
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.49,0:16:20.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我交给你的是复印稿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.41,0:16:23.25,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎么可能给十丸院先生手稿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.54,0:16:24.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,能干
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.16,0:16:23.21,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\fs65\bord3\frz270\c&HDCB9BB&\3c&H000000&\pos(1594,462)}能干
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.21,0:16:23.25,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\fs65\bord3\frz270\c&HDCB9BB&\3c&H000000&\pos(1292,460)}能干
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.25,0:16:23.29,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\fs65\bord3\frz270\c&HDCB9BB&\3c&H000000&\pos(1152,466)}能干
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.29,0:16:23.33,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\fs65\bord3\frz270\c&HDCB9BB&\3c&H000000&\pos(1100,466)}能干
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.33,0:16:24.58,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\fs65\bord3\frz270\c&HDCB9BB&\3c&H000000&\pos(1086,464)}能干
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.17,0:16:27.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就先不说了  让他好好反省一阵子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.46,0:16:29.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,哭唧唧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.25,0:16:33.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,说起来  还不是老师您没有用电子画板我才成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.26,0:16:35.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那个我不用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.51,0:16:38.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我感觉还是传统的更有灵魂一些
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.81,0:16:41.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,离最终回也不远了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.10,0:16:45.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,最终回？您指的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.40,0:16:50.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我也打算去远处逛两周
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.07,0:16:53.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我也订好了取材旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.20,0:16:55.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,接下来有好多有趣的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.41,0:16:57.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,大伙儿  高兴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.16,0:17:01.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,紧身裤不会完结了  要继续连载
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.04,0:17:07.04,kakushigoto in 5,,0,0,0,,{\c&H7C685E&\pos(1038,412)}风之紧身裤\N{\fs60}\h读者调查问卷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.50,0:17:09.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,结果只是一瞬间的高光时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.13,0:17:12.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就算责编再怎么优秀  也是有极限的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:15.55,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\pos(864,340)}会议中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.88,0:17:18.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你说的生日聚会  是你朋友的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:19.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.31,0:17:22.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.27,0:17:26.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以  关于生日聚会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.35,0:17:29.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我去向她表明拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.86,0:17:32.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是  如果我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.19,0:17:35.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就得招待她们来我的生日聚会了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.53,0:17:37.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我们家不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:41.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,只有爸爸你一个人准备太辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:43.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,难道  又是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:45.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,炸鸡块
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.29,0:17:47.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,炸鸡块?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.46,0:17:48.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.63,0:17:54.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,因为大家定好了  要带自己做的菜去参加生日聚会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.63,0:17:58.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以我觉得生日聚会一定少不了炸鸡块
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.22,0:18:03.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是  我还不能一个人炸东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.56,0:18:08.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以我想  能不能让爸爸你帮帮我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:17.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这样啊  原来是炸鸡块啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.61,0:18:18.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.36,0:18:21.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我们一起炸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:26.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸也得为了准备你的生日聚会  还得不断练习
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.00,0:18:27.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,谢谢爸爸
